                <head>No. 656.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 28, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Am without reply to my telegram to you of 26th. Have reason to assure you that
                    this government is ready to yield our terms of reparation. Hope to announce this
                    result to you this afternoon.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>SICKLES.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
